# project/emscripten

Emscripten build configuration for Minecraft web target.

- **build_web.ps1** тАУ main build script. Sources `../../../emsdk/emsdk_env.ps1`, compiles `../../src/*.cpp` (excluding platform-specific), links with `mc_platform.js`, `shell.html`, preloads `../../data@/data`.
- **mc_platform.js** тАУ Emscripten JS library. Exposes `mcShowCreateWorldDialog`, `idbfsReady`, `syncSaves`; uses `mergeInto(LibraryManager.library, ...)`.
- **shell.html** тАУ Emscripten shell. Contains `{{{ SCRIPT }}}` placeholder; handles touch/mouse, pointer lock, service worker.
- **manifest.json**, **sw.js** тАУ PWA manifest and service worker for offline/caching.
- Link flags: `-sASYNCIFY=1`, `-sUSE_SDL=2`, `-sLEGACY_GL_EMULATION=1`, `-lopenal`, `-lidbfs.js`, `--preload-file ../../data@/data`.
